// NavySection.astro
---

<div class="relative bg-cover bg-center text-white  bg-black py-12" style="background-image: url('/india-map-background.png');">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black opacity-60"></div>
  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center py-12 px-6 md:px-16">
    <div class="md:w-1/2">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">Official Solutions Provider: Indian Navy</h2>
      <div class="border-b-4 border-teal-400 w-16 mb-4"></div>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Our dedication and accomplishments were formally acknowledged when we attained the prestigious Indian Navy vendor approval on the 24th of May 2023. This significant milestone signifies our recognition as a trusted and authorized partner, empowering us to serve all four Naval Commands:
      </p>
      <ul class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <li class="mb-2">Western Naval Command - Mumbai</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Eastern Naval Command - Visakhapatnam</li>
        <li class="mb-2">Southern Naval Command - Kochi</li>
        <li class="text-teal-400">Tri-services Command - Port Blair</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">This underscores our comprehensive reach and steadfast commitment to bolstering the Indian Navy across diverse geographical locations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-1/2 mt-8 md:mt-0 flex justify-center">
      <img src="/india-map.png" alt="Indian Navy Commands" class="w-full md:w-3/4" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
